{"tid":1296796,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷《奧萊報》:一旦小花禁賽,阿根廷就轉去歐國聯. 歐足總:阿根廷可以黎睇波","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:48:48.000Z","uid":25345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3efcbe042c251efbd5c6eab4861e6cc2e699e4d6","tid":1296796,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2019/07/08/589b56be61d44d629df412bef6214fa0.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.ws.126.net%2F2019%2F07%2F08%2F589b56be61d44d629df412bef6214fa0.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=264d0d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在美洲杯中，阿根廷隊認為自己遭到了裁判和南美足聯的針對。公開放炮的梅西，則有可能遭到重罰。在這種情況下，阿根廷媒體為球隊找到了退路。《奧萊報》今天指出，阿根廷一旦遭遇重罰，就有可能轉投歐足聯。該報還指出，阿根廷此前曾拒絕應歐足聯邀請參加歐國聯，但如今有可能重新考慮加入這一賽事。結果幾個小時之後，歐足聯就做出了官方回應，阿根廷媒體的說法被完全否認。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邀請阿根廷加入歐足聯並參加歐國聯比賽？歐足聯對此事進行了辟謠：&ldquo;關於邀請阿根廷參加歐國聯比賽的消息並不是事實，邀請阿根廷加入歐足聯的消息同樣如此。歐足聯從未在這個問題上進行過討論，而且永遠也不會這樣做。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n在歐足聯看來，阿根廷頂多只能充當歐洲賽事的看客：&ldquo;本著友誼第一的精神，作為一個具有包容性的組織，歐足聯願意邀請阿根廷作為特殊嘉賓，在任何時候觀看任何歐足聯賽事。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐足聯的官方回應，斷了阿根廷&ldquo;入籍&rdquo;歐洲的可能性。這也就意味著，無論梅西遭到怎樣的追加處罰，阿根廷要麼留在南美足聯內部接受處罰，要麼就只能爭取加入其他水准更低的大洲了。"},{"pid":"b58a372a56d1d6d1c954fe4f70c38a2d75958d5e","tid":1296796,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e369d23d2f245a4d23f7ac94045d963611de27","tid":1296796,"uid":5006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"亞軍廷連美洲盃都踢唔掂<br />\n去歐國聯比人屈臭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb4ab96115e65399cab43c8b5e82771f78e4eff","tid":1296796,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3e369d23d2f245a4d23f7ac94045d963611de27","tid":1296796,"uid":5006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"亞軍廷連美洲盃都踢唔掂<br />\n去歐國聯比人屈臭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"花迷話美洲盃競爭大過歐國盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e059e6412468c1330e735df58a62aaa34e1aaec","tid":1296796,"uid":173456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5cb4ab96115e65399cab43c8b5e82771f78e4eff","tid":1296796,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3e369d23d2f245a4d23f7ac94045d963611de27","tid":1296796,"uid":5006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"亞軍廷連美洲盃都踢唔掂<br />\n去歐國聯比人屈臭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"花迷話美洲盃競爭大過歐國盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:45:26.000Z","msg":"花迷話只要美斯願意就會有冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f961fb41c2462316c192a7c3542ef668ecdbfb","tid":1296796,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"美洲冇得踢黎亞洲啦 應該拿到盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2228116abb811772e8216d82e4a3d1ea64a9ec28","